<P>
   IMPEACH _ WASHINGTON _ The House Judiciary Committee grants the
White House an additional 30 hours to mold a defense for President
Clinton, as it appeared likely that the House would approve at
least one article of impeachment against the president. (Carr, Cox
News Service)
