<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-06 19:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5490 &Cx1f; tta-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LAYOFFS-NEWSTYLE-ART-     12-06 1115
