<DOCNO> NYT19981206.0153 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-06 20:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5557 &Cx1f; tta-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NATO-MEETING-1     12-06 1175
</HEADER>
